video_name: 🇬🇷 Avgolemono | Soups So Good It Can Cure Any Sickness Ep. 14 INGREDIENTS:  Greek Avgolemono: - 5-8 chicken thigh bone in, (can also be 1 whole chicken) - Olive oil - 1 tbsp of Italian seasoning - 1 whole onion, diced - 5-10 garlic cloves, minced - 3/4 cup celery, diced - 1 carrot, diced - Chicken broth as needed - ¾ cup orzo pasta  - Bay leaves (optional) - Salt and pepper to taste Avgolemono Mixture: - 4 eggs - The juice of 2-3 lemons - lemon zesr - reserved broth from the Avgolemono Soup INSTRUCTIONS:  - Start by seasoning your chicken and searing it in a pot with a bit of oil until browned. Once golden, set the chicken aside for later. - In the same pot, sauté your vegetables until fragrant, then add Italian seasoning. add your chicken broth. - Return the chicken to the pot and set it to a gentle simmer for 45 minutes, or until tender. Once done, shred the chicken and add back to the soup. - Add the orzo pasta and let it cook in the broth for 8–10 minutes - Meanwhile, prepare the avgolemono mixture. In a separate bowl, whisk together eggs and add lemon juice/zest. To temper, pour in a thin stream a bit of hot soup while whisking constantly. This will prevent the eggs from scrambling. - Once tempered, gently stir the avgolemono mixture back into the pot. - Serve your soup hot, garnished with fresh dill/parsley and a drizzle of olive oil and enjoy! #Soups #asmr #ASMRCooking

video_name: Italian Wedding Soup | Soups So Good It Can Cure Any Sickness Ep. 12 INGREDIENTS: Meatballs: - 350g lean ground beef - 3 pcs Italian sausage, casings removed - 2 large egg - ⅓ cup of parsley, chopped - ½ tbsp of garlic powder - 2 tbsp parsley, finely chopped  - ½ cup bread crumbs - ⅓ cup grated parmesan cheese - Salt and pepper to taste Italian Wedding Soup Base: - Olive oil - 1 yellow onion, diced - 8-12 cloves of garlic, diced - 2 large carrots, diced - 2 stalks celery, diced - ½ cup of white wine - 3 cups chicken broth - 3 cups beef broth - 2 bay leaves - Salt and pepper to taste - 1 cup small pasta (orzo) - 3 cups spinach, chopped INSTRUCTIONS:  - Start by making your meatballs. video_name: Popcorn Chicken 🐓🍿 INGREDIENTS: Popcorn chicken: - 1kg of chicken thigh fillet, cubed - 2 tbsp of garlic powder - 2 tbsp hot sauce (here i’m using Cholula) - 2 tbsp old bay seasoning - 2 eggs - 1:1 ratio of rice and all purpose flour - Salt & pepper to taste - 1 cup of soaked tapioca pearls (soak for 1hr) Honey Mustard Dip: - 1 cup mayonnaise - ⅓ cup of mustard - ⅓ cup of honey - The juice of one lemon INSTRUCTIONS: - Start by slicing your chicken thighs into cubes, and adding them into a bowl. add two eggs, and season with garlic powder ,old bay, hot sauce, and worcestershire sauce. Add equal parts rice flour and all-purpose flour and mix by hand. Set aside and allow to marinate while prepping your tapioca pearls. - Soak your tapioca pearls in water and allow them to soften for around 1hr. Once softened add it into the bowl. - Fry at 165°C in small batches until golden brown and crispy, about 6–8 minutes depending on size. Double fry at 180C for 2-3 mins for maximum crispyness. - Serve with the sauce and enjoy! #asmr #asmrcooking

video_name: Lamb in Apricot Sauce | Medieval Meals Ep. 12 This dish carries inspiration from the Silk Roads, where spices, fruits, and ideas flowed into Europe. Far from being isolated, medieval tables were shaped by trade routes that stretched across continents. Additionally for any depictions made of barbarians it’s important to note the popular image of wild raiders was just a fantasy. Barbarians in a traditional sense were skilled traders, craftsmen, and farmers — their lives far richer and more complex than the myths suggest. Disclaimer: While the content is inspired by real research from medieval times, the video incorporates elements of medieval faction and fiction for the purposes of entertainment. Researchers: - Igi Gomez Resources: - Adamson, M. W. (2004). Food in medieval times. Greenwood Press. - Hieatt, C. B., Butler, B., & Hosington, S. (1976). Pleyn delit: Medieval cookery for modern cooks. University of Toronto Press. INGREDIENTS:  - 2 lbs boneless lamb, in chunks - 1 lbs of lamb shanks, scored - Salt and pepper to taste - Oil or lard for frying - 1–2 onions, chopped - ⅓ cup of ground almonds - ½ lb dried apricots - Beef broth til pot is filled - 1 tsp ground ginger - 1 tsp ground coriander  INSTRUCTIONS:  - Start by scoring your lamb shanks and cutting your meat into bite sized cubes. Fry them in lard or oil until golden and set aside.  - In the same pot, saute onions until softened, and add ground almonds, apricots and beef stock. Season with ginger, coriander, pepper, and salt, and place in a heat-safe blender. Blend until thick. - Return the meat into the pot, and simmer for 20-30 minutes. Serve and enjoy! #medievalfood #darkfantasy #medieval #lightfantasy

video_name: 🥪Mechadito Ingredientes: 1kg de Roast Beef 1 Morron 1 Cebolla 2 dientes de ajo 1 Puñado de sal 1 Lata de Tomate Agua Lo dejas cocinando por minimo 2 horas. video_name: Matambrito de Cerdo al Verdeo con Papas Españolas La primer comida que recuerdo 500gr Matambrito de Cerdo 2 Cebollas de verdeo 200ml de Crema 2 Papas Aceite y Sal El matmbrito lo cocinas desde la sarten fria a fuego medio/bajo. No se va a secar porque tiene una buena cantidad de grasa y al mismo tiempo se va a dorar. La crema es solamente calentarla un poco, no la cocines demasiado. Evita que empiecen a salir muchas burbujas. Y las papas yo la tire asi nomas. Sin pasar por agua ni nada, con el aceite a temperatura media deberian ir dorandose y quedar crocantes. Revolvelas un poco para que no se peguen. #receta #recetasfaciles #recipesoftiktok #fyp

bio: No es otra pagina de recetas más.
video_name: Este Pollo viene con Sorpresa Ingredientes: 1.5kg de Pollo (Pata y muslo) 2 Tazas de Harina de trigo 1/2 Taza de Fecula de maiz 2 Cucharaditas de Polvo de hornear Especias: (Podes poner lo que quieras) 2 Cucharadas de sal 1 Cucharada de Ajo en polvo 1 Cucharada de Pimenton 1 Cucharada de Tomillo 1 Cucharada de Pimienta 2 Huevos 100ml de Agua (Es medio a ojo) Para la salsa: Perejil 1/2 cebolla 1/2 diente de ajo 1 cebolla de verdeo 2 Cucharadas de Mayonesa 4 Cucharas de Yogur Neutro Sal y Pimienta Jugo de Medio limon Freir en aceite a 160°C 18 minutos y dejar enfriar. (Tarda en bajar la temperatura, asi que se sigue cocinando y se va poniendo mas crocante) Es importante que haya bastante aceite y no pongas mucho pollo porque sino lo vas a enfriar demasiado. Masomenos por 1lt de aceite mete 3/4 piezas Podes usar el truco de la cucharada de madera para medir la temperatura O si lo pones a fuego medio y precalentas por 15 minutos va estar bien. #fyp #recipesoftiktok #recetasfaciles #receta

bio: No es otra pagina de recetas más.
video_name: Ramen Un par de aclaraciones previas.  El ramen es una comida que lleva tiempo, hay muchas versiones pero todas tienen como protagonistas caldos que llevan mucha coccion. Esta es una version rapida porque a mi tampoco me tienta la idea de estar 3 dias para hacer unos fideos. Ingredientes:  1kg de Cerdo (Usé Bondiola) Huevo duro Hongos (Usé champigniones, lo ideal es shitake pero no se consiguen facil) Fideos  Verdeo crudo picado Para el Caldo: Doras la carne 6 Dientes de Ajo 1 Jengibre 1 Cebolla de verdeo 1 Puerro 1 Cebolla 1/2 Taza de Azucar 1 Taza de Salsa de Soja Lo tapas con agua (Minimo 1,5 lt agrega) Dejas hervir a fuego bajo por 1 hora y media. Despues colas el caldo y metes lo hongos a remojar ahi mientras cortas la carne y preparas los fideos. Las cosas clave: Si el caldo te quedo muy fuerte (se redujo mucho) podes agregarle agua o al momento de servir en el plato una cucharada del agua de los fideos. Y si usaste el polvo saborizante que viene de los fideos ramen comprados todavia mejor. Para que los huevos queden así. Los pones al fuego con agua fria y en cuanto hierve con ganas contas 6 minutos exacto. Los sacas y rapido en agua helada. La idea de atar la carne es para que no pierda la forma circular. #receta #recetasfaciles #recipesoftiktok #fyp

video_name: Asi es El Verdadero Goulash Ingredientes para 4: 1kg de Carne  2 Cebollas  4 Cucharadas de Paprika 1 Cucharada de Semillas de Kummel 1/2 Morron 1 Tomate 800gr de Papa Caldo/agua y Sal Para lo Csipetke: 1 huevo 200gr de Harina Sal Haces la masa, la pellizcas y los tiras 5 minutos a cocinar Claves: Es importante ir mirando el goulash para que no se quede sin agua. Al tener papa no es necesario hacer tanto csipetke Usa una olla grande, sino va a desbordar. Claramente podes reemplazar la paprika por pimenton y el kummel por hinojo si no conseguis. Desde que tiras la papa son aprox. 30 minutos mas. Lo importante es que lo pruebes. #receta #recetasfaciles #recipesoftiktok #fyp

video_name: Maybe you can help me think this through? When I started six years ago, I planned to hire a chef who could bring my ideas to life better than I could. I’d run the floor and manage the service side, which is also my area of strength. The bigger vision was to expand quickly and eventually open a brunch café–bakery concept. But fast forward to now, and things have considerably changed. I don’t see myself necessarily doing a brunch spot anymore and gruelling away on scrambled eggs 7 days a week or leading service (at least not right away). If anything now, I see myself more than ever in the kitchen instead. There are obvious trade-offs. It could slow down my growth with the initial launch, and I might not be as visible as I originally planned. But if I prove myself in the kitchen and do it well, it solidifies my credibility beyond just “playing” with fruits and with flashy edits to, a perhaps, legitimate, skilled chef. So, as I begin to double down more on my future vision, I’ve been increasingly torn about where to focus now, whether to begin with pastry or a restaurant concept, and which one should become the flagship aka driving force that sets the tone for everything to come. Pastry, brunch, cafe, bakery fine dining, pub... what do you see first?

video_name: nutella stuffed chocolate chip cookies !    recipe:   1/2 cup butter, browned (113g) 1/4 cup granulated sugar (50g) 1/2 cup dark brown sugar, packed (100g) 1 large egg  1 tsp vanilla extract (5g) 1 1/2 cups all-purpose flour (190g) 1/2 tsp baking soda (3g) 1/4 tsp salt (1g) chocolate chips(measure with your heart idk, i used @Nestle Toll House ) 6 tbsp nutella(90g)(i used 3 for the cookies & the rest to drizzle.)  instructions- brown the butter & let cool slightly. in a bowl whisk together the browned butter & sugars until glossy. add the egg & vanilla and mix until combined. add in the flour, baking soda, and salt and fold gently then add chocolate chips and fold until the dough comes together. scoop dough balls, flatten slightly, place a frozen nutella scoop in the center, and roll it back up. bake at 350°f (175°c) for 11–13 minutes until golden on the edges but soft in the middle.( i made 3 big cookies & 6 small ones. the bigger ones cooked for 15-17 minutes. )    #nutella #chocolatechipcookies #cookies #fyp #baking

video_name: chocolate nutella cinnamon rolls 🤎 these tasted like chocolate donuts ??    recipe:   3/4 cup warm milk(180g) 3 tbsp melted butter(43g) 4 tbsp granulated sugar(50g) 2 1/4 tsp yeast(7g) 1 egg 1 yolk 3 cups of flour(360g) 3 tbsp cocoa powder(18g) 1/4 tsp salt(1.5g) 1/4 cup heavy cream(60g) ( goes on top before baking )    mix your warm milk. sugar, and yeast and let sit for 5-10 minutes. once frothy add in your egg and butter and mix. then add in your dry ingredients and continue mixing until it becomes a shaggy dough. knead until a smooth dough forms. ( you may need to add a bit more flour. but i reccomend coating your hands in olive oil and kneading that way. ) let sit in an oiled bowl covered for 1 hr. after the hour punch the dough down and roll it out.    filling:   1/4 cup melted butter(57g)  1 cup brown sugar(200g) 3 tsp cinnamon(7-8g) 2-3 tbsp nutella (40-60g) 1 tbsp cocoa powder(6g)   mix until combined. let your butter cool a tad bit just so it doesn’t melt the sugar. spread over rolled out dough & roll them up. cut your desired cinnamon roll sizes & let sit for another 30 minutes. pour heavy cream over top of rolls and bake at 350•F for about 25-35 minutes. ( can vary depending on your oven ) while they’re still warm spread nutella over top. or use a different frosting recipe( i didn’t like the idea of chocolate cream cheese frosting idk )    #chocolate #cinnamonroll #nutella #bakingrecipe #fyp

video_name: crispy cheesy garlic potato balls!! this time they’re super crispy :D    easy recipe:   5 yellow potatoes 5 tbsp cornstarch (plus some for rolling) (40g) 1 tsp salt (adjust to taste) (6g) 1 tsp garlic powder (3g) 1/2 tsp onion powder (1.5g) 1/4 tsp black pepper (0.5g) 1 tsp parsley (1g)   cut & peel your potatoes. then boil until they’re fork tender. add to a bowl and mash up until smooth. then add in your spices & cornstarch, mix until a dough forms. seperate your dough ( i did 1 heaping tbsp for each, i got 9 balls ) then flatten & add your cheese. roll them back up and roll in cornstarch( don’t skip this step, you want to lightly coat them it helps with the crispy skin ). let freeze for 30 mins - 1 hr. then fry until golden brown on each side. let dry on a rack a bit before eating.    #cheese #garlic #potatoes #Recipe #baking

video_name: happy october 1st !! 🍁 pumpkin pie cookies, crumbl dupeee?  recipe: yields about 10 cookies. 1/2 cup softened butter(113g) es 1/2 cup granulated sugar 100g) 1/4 cup brown sugar 50g) 1 egg yolk 1/2 tsp vanilla paste(2g) 11/4 cup flour(156g) 1/4 tsp salt(1.5g) 1/4 tsp baking powder (1g) 1 tbsp milk(15g) mix your butter & sugars until combined, then add your egg & vanilla, mix and fold in your dry ingredients (i added milk to mine because i felt the dough was a bit too dry, if you're looking for a more puffy cookie, don't add the milk & add 1/2 tsp baking powder instead of 1/4. ) seperate your dough balls (i did about 1 heaping tbsp for each cookie ) and place on a baking sheet i tried shaping mine but it did not stay after baking LOL) bake at 350•F for about 11-12 minutes ( depending on how big your cookies are ) bake until the edges are set but the middle is slightly soft. after you take them out, while they're still warm, shape them (optional). let cool and add filling ! pumpkin filling: 8 oz cream cheese 1/2 cup pumpkin puree 4 tbsp brown sugar 1 tsp pumpkin pie spice ( or 1/2 tsp nutmeg, 1/8 tsp all spice, & ginger ) 1 tsp cinnamon place the pumpkin puree in a clean piece of cheesecloth, gently squeeze to remove excess liquid. repeat until the pumpkin feels thick & not watery, (you can add more pumpkin to taste ). add to bowl with cream cheese & other spices & mix until fluffy & combined. set aside until your ready to use (refrigerate ) homemade whipped cream: 1 cup heavy whipping cream (240g) 2-3 tbsp powdered sugar 15-30g) (adjust to taste) 1 tsp vanilla (5g) whip until stiff peaks form and pipe over cookies!   #pumpkinpie #cookies #october #fallbaking #recipe

video_name: This ain’t your average one-pan pasta🍝  Creamy, easy, tangy, with a subtle Cajun kick 🌶️The pasta that does it all ✨ 📍Tag your pasta bestie & save this recipe for your next craving💗 🍝 Hailey’s One-Pan Creamy Cajun Tomato Pasta 📝 Ingredients (2 servings) •	2 Tbsp olive oil •	6 oz pasta noodles (170g) •	7 oz cherry tomatoes, halved (200g) •	½ onion, sliced •	2 strips bacon, sliced •	4 baby bella mushrooms, sliced •	2 handfuls spinach •	3 cloves garlic, thinly sliced •	1 tsp Italian seasoning •	½ Tbsp Cajun seasoning •	1 tsp–½ Tbsp sugar (adjust to tomato acidity & taste) •	Salt & pepper, to taste •	300ml whipping cream (~1 ¼ cups) •	1 Tbsp tomato paste •	5.3 oz beef broth (~150g / ⅔ cup) •	⅓ cup grated Parmesan cheese (~1 oz / 28g) ⸻ 👩‍🍳 Instructions 1.	Heat the base Warm olive oil in a large pan over medium heat. 2.	Layer the ingredients Place pasta in the center of the pan. Arrange cherry tomatoes, onion, bacon, and mushrooms around it. Scatter garlic on top. 3.	Build the flavor Add Italian seasoning, Cajun seasoning, and sugar. Spoon tomato paste over the pasta and veggies. 4.	Simmer the pasta Pour in beef broth and whipping cream. Cover and cook for 8–10 minutes, until pasta is almost al dente. Remove lid, stir gently, and add a splash of water or broth if needed.	 5.	Finish with greens & cheese Stir in spinach until just wilted. Add Parmesan and mix until sauce is smooth and creamy. Adjust with salt & pepper. 6.	Serve hot Garnish with extra Parmesan or a sprinkle of Cajun seasoning. Enjoy straight from the pan! ⸻ 💡 Tip A touch of sugar (1 tsp–½ Tbsp) balances the tomatoes’ acidity and enhances the depth of the sauce. #onepanpasta #asmrfood #mukbang #EasyRecipe #fyp @centofinefoods

video_name: This ain’t your average one-pan pasta 🍝 Creamy, garlicky, and loaded with juicy shrimp—all in ONE pan ✨ Perfect for your next weeknight craving 🔥 📍Tag your pasta bestie & save this recipe for a lazy-day treat 💗 ✨ Hailey’s One-Pan Creamy Shrimp Pasta 📝 Ingredients (2 servings) Base •	2 Tbsp olive oil •	6 oz (170 g) pasta •	8–10 large shrimp, peeled & deveined •	3-4 cloves garlic, thinly sliced •	½ onion, sliced •	4 baby bella mushrooms, sliced •	2 handfuls baby spinach •	1 Tbsp butter •	300 ml heavy cream •	200 ml chicken broth •	½ cup Parmesan cheese •	1 tsp Italian seasoning •	Salt & black pepper, to taste •	Fresh parsley, for garnish Shrimp Seasoning •	½ tsp paprika •	1 tsp garlic powder •	1 tsp onion powder •	1 Tbsp olive oil •	Salt & black pepper, to taste ⸻ 👩‍🍳 Instructions 1. Heat the base Warm olive oil in a large pan over medium heat. 2. Arrange the layers Place pasta in the center of the pan. Surround with onion, mushrooms, seasoned shrimp, and garlic. 3. Build the flavor Sprinkle in Italian seasoning, paprika, onion powder, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper. 4. Simmer the pasta Add butter, then pour in chicken broth and heavy cream. Cover and bring to a gentle boil. •	Stir occasionally to prevent sticking. •	Flip shrimp halfway through, then cover again for 5 minutes. •	Remove shrimp to avoid overcooking, and stir pasta gently. 5. Make it creamy Stir in Parmesan until the sauce is smooth and glossy. Continue cooking 3–5 minutes, until pasta is al dente. Add spinach and stir until just wilted. Adjust seasoning if needed. 6. Serve hot Finish with extra Parmesan, chili flakes, and fresh parsley. Serve immediately and enjoy! #onepanpasta #asmrfood #mukbang #easyrecipe #fyp

Boil the noodles Bring 1.5 cups of water to a boil. Add noodles and cook until just tender. 👉 Don’t forget to save the noodle water—it’s key for the broth! 2. Create the broth Add noodles, then pour in about ¾ cup of hot noodle water. Swirl gently until the broth turns creamy. 4.	Top it off (optional but highly recommended!) video_name: This Bread Will Change Your Life 🤯🍞 Crispy on the outside, gooey + cheesy inside… and that cheese pull is UNREAL 🔥🧀 Every cut drenched in rich garlic honey butter — garlicky, buttery, and sweet all at once ✨ Finished with a sprinkle of cinnamon + a drizzle of maple 🍯 Inspired by the bread I loved at cafés in Korea — but with a cheesy twist 💗 📍Tag your bestie & SAVE this recipe — you’ll thank me later 💗 ✨ Hailey’s Cheesy Garlic Honey Butter Bread 📝 Ingredients  •	3 slices white bread •	2 slices mozzarella cheese (or shredded) •	3 tbsp unsalted butter •	1 tbsp honey •	1 tbsp minced garlic •	2 pinches salt  •	Dried parsley (for garnish) •	Cinnamon powder (for garnish) •	Powdered sugar (optional) •	Maple syrup (for drizzle) ⸻ 🍯 Instructions 1.	Stack the bread •	Layer: bread → mozzarella → bread → mozzarella → bread. •	Creates a triple-layer cheese sandwich. 2.	Score the bread •	Cut the top into a 3×3 grid (9 squares). •	Don’t slice all the way through — just deep enough so it pulls apart easily. 3.	Make the garlic honey butter sauce •	In a bowl, mix butter, honey, garlic, salt, and parsley. •	Microwave ~20 sec until melted, then stir until silky smooth. 4.	Brush generously •	Let the sauce drip deep into the cuts and brush over the top until glossy. 5.	Air fry (or bake) •	Air fry at 350°F (175°C) for 7–9 minutes until golden + crispy. •	Or bake at 375°F (190°C) for 8–10 minutes. 6.	Serve & finish •	Sprinkle with cinnamon and a light dusting of powdered sugar (optional). Add a touch of parsley for garnish (optional), then drizzle with maple syrup. •	Pull apart, stretch that cheese, and enjoy 🧀✨ #garlicbread #asmrfood #mukbang #koreanfood #fyp @Land O’Lakes

video_name: This ain’t your average Alfredo pasta ✨ Caramelized onion, garlic and chicken bouillon take it NEXT LEVEL🧅🔥 Creamy, cheesy, UNREAL 🤌🍤 This shrimp Alfredo hits DIFFERENT 😮‍💨🍝 📍Tag your pasta bestie & save this recipe for your next craving💗 ✨ Hailey’s Creamy Shrimp Alfredo Ingredients Main •	2 Tbsp butter •	12–14 peeled shrimp •	2 cups heavy whipping cream •	6 oz linguine (or pasta of choice) •	1 onion, thinly sliced •	4 cloves garlic, minced •	½ Tbsp chicken bouillon •	¾ cup grated Parmesan cheese •	1 handful baby spinach (optional) •	3 baby bella mushrooms, sliced (optional) •	½ cup reserved pasta water •	Fresh parsley, to taste •	Olive oil Shrimp Seasoning •	1 tsp paprika powder •	1 tsp garlic powder •	1 tsp onion powder •	1 tsp Italian seasoning (optional) •	1 Tbsp olive oil •	Salt, to taste •	Black pepper, to taste ⸻ Instructions 1. Season the Shrimp In a bowl, coat the shrimp with paprika, garlic powder, onion powder, olive oil, salt, and black pepper. Mix well and set aside. 2. Cook the Pasta Boil the linguine in salted water until al dente. Reserve about ½ cup of pasta water, then drain. 3. Cook the Shrimp In a large pan, melt 1 Tbsp butter with a drizzle of olive oil over medium heat. Add the seasoned shrimp and cook until pink, about 2–3 minutes per side. Remove from the pan, sprinkle with parsley, and set aside. 4. Caramelize the Onion In the same pan, add another drizzle of olive oil and melt the remaining 1 Tbsp butter. Sauté the onion and garlic over medium heat until softened and golden. Add spinach and mushrooms (if using) and cook until tender. 5. Make the Sauce Pour in the heavy cream, chicken bouillon, and Parmesan cheese. Stir until smooth and creamy. Add pasta water as needed to adjust consistency. Season with salt and black pepper to taste. 6. Finish & Serve Toss the pasta into the sauce until fully coated. Return the shrimp to the pan and mix gently. Garnish with fresh parsley and extra Parmesan before serving. #creamypasta #asmrfood #mukbang #shrimpalfredo #fyp

video_name: The pasta that tamed a raging king 👑🔥 Doenjang + spinach pesto = royal levels of umami 🌿🍝 Straight out of a K-drama scene ✨ Honestly, it wasn’t really my type of flavor—I think adding cream would make it even better. But since the chef in the drama didn’t use it, I kept it authentic. Still, it’s definitely worth trying if you’re a K-drama fan 💫 Tag your K-drama buddy & save this recipe for your next Bon Appétit, Your Majesty night! 🍴 Inspired by the Korean drama Bon Appétit, Your Majesty 🎬 🌿 Doenjang Pasta with Spinach Pesto Ingredients Pasta & Sauce 	•	6 oz spaghetti or linguine 	•	10–12 clams 	•	5 mussels (optional) 	•	2 Tbsp salt (for clam cleaning) 	•	1 Tbsp doenjang (Korean soybean paste) 	•	1 ½ Tbsp minced garlic 	•	1 Tbsp perilla oil 	•	½ Tbsp sugar 	•	2 Tbsp vodka or cooking wine 	•	1 Tbsp chili crisp 	•	Pinch of MSG (optional) 	•	Cornstarch slurry (1 Tbsp cornstarch + 2 Tbsp cold water) 	•	Black pepper, to taste Spinach Pesto 	•	3 handfuls spinach 	•	3 Tbsp pine nuts 	•	2 Tbsp grated Parmesan 	•	1 Tbsp perilla oil ⸻ Instructions 1. Purge the clams Place clams in a bowl with 4 cups of water and 2 Tbsp salt. Add a stainless steel spoon, cover with foil, and let sit for 30–60 minutes. (The spoon helps the clams release sand more effectively.) While waiting, prep the other ingredients. 2. Make the spinach pesto Blend spinach, pine nuts, Parmesan, and perilla oil until smooth. Set aside. 3. Cook the pasta Boil the pasta in salted water until al dente. Reserve 1 cup of the noodle water before draining. 4. Build the doenjang sauce Heat perilla oil in a pan over low heat. Add garlic, doenjang, and 2 Tbsp water. Sauté until fragrant. Add clams (and mussels, if using), chili crisp, sugar, vodka, and 1 cup of reserved noodle water. Simmer for 5 minutes. Stir in the cornstarch slurry to slightly thicken. 5. Combine Add the pasta and a pinch of MSG (if using) to the pan. Toss until evenly coated in the doenjang sauce. Season with black pepper. 6. Plate & finish Twirl the pasta onto a plate. Spoon spinach pesto over the top, garnish with crushed pine nuts, and mix well before eating. ⸻ 💡 Tip: Not a fan of clams? Swap them for shrimp or bacon.  (Bacon is my favorite—it’s quick, easy, and adds a rich, savory depth without the hassle of cleaning clams.) #doenjangpasta #bonappetityourmajesty #asmrfood #mukbang #fyp

video_name: Would you try this or skip? 👀 The Shin Ramyun you never knew you needed🔥Creamy, spicy, and dangerously addictive ✨ 📍 Tag your ramen buddy & save this for your next cozy noodle night 💗 ✨ Hailey’s Addictive Shin Ramen 🍜 📝 Ingredients •	1 pack Shin Ramyun •	2 cups water •	1 egg yolk •	½ Tbsp minced garlic •	½ Tbsp chopped spring onion •	1 Tbsp mayonnaise •	Your choice of protein–seafood or meat (optional) •	1–2 soft-boiled eggs (optional) •	A few bok choy leaves (optional) •	2 Tbsp chili oil ⸻ 👩🏻‍🍳 Instructions 1.	Boil the noodles Bring 2 cups of water to a boil. Add the noodles and cook until tender. Transfer the noodles to a bowl, saving the hot noodle water—it will be the base for your creamy broth. 2. Make the creamy sauce In a bowl, whisk together the egg yolk, Shin Ramyun seasoning, minced garlic, chopped spring onion, mayonnaise, and sizzling chili oil until smooth and combined. 4.	Create the broth Pour in about 1½ cups of the reserved hot noodle water. Stir gently until the sauce becomes rich and creamy. 5.	Add the noodles Return the noodles to the bowl and toss until evenly coated in the spicy, creamy sauce. 6.	Top it off (optional but highly recommended!) Finish with a soft-boiled egg, your chosen protein, bok choy, and a final drizzle of chili oil for an extra flavor kick. ⸻ 💡 Tip: Adjust the noodle water to get your perfect broth—thick and saucy, or light and soupy. Not a fan of raw egg yolk? Just skip it! #ramenhack #asmrfood #koreanfood #mukbang #fyp @Nongshim USA @Nongshim Global

Geçen hafta Kıbrıs’taydım ve bu güzel adanın güzelliklerini sizinle de paylaşmak istedim. 😊 📍KARPAZ  Burası Kıbrıs haritasına bakınca hepimizin dikkatini çeken, Türkiye’ye doğru parmak gibi uzanan, ince, uzun yarımada. El değmemiş doğası, tarihi kalıntıları, Türklerle Rumların bir arada yaşadığı köyleri, özgürce dolaşan sevimli yabani eşekleri ve Altınkum Plajı’yla benim Kıbrısta en sevdiğim yer. 📍GİRNE 7. yüzyıldan kalma kalesi, hemen önündeki ç balıkçı tekneleri ve keyifli mekanlarıyla adanın en  hareketli yerlerinden biri. Eğlencesiyle ünlü birçok otel de Girne ve çevresinde yer alıyor. 📍BELLAPAIS KÖYÜ VE MANASTIRI Girne’nin tepelerinde şirin bir köy. 760 yıllık gotik manastırından manzara şahane. 📍KARMİ KÖYÜ Birbirinden güzel evlere ve kapılara sahip bu köyün sokak aralarında kaybolup bol bol fotoğraf çekebilirsiniz. Köyde mola verebileceğiniz keyifli bir kahveci de var. 📍LEFKOŞA Dünyanın ikiye bölünmüş tek başkenti. Bir yarısı KKTC’de, diğer yarısı ise Rum Kesimi’nde. Arabahmet Mahallesi’ninin tarihi sokaklarında mutlaka dolaşmanız, Büyük Han’ı ve Selimiye Camii’ni görmeniz lazım. 📍GAZİMAĞUSA Karpaz’dan sonra en güzel sahiller Gazimağusa’da. Gotik mimarideoi Lala Mustafa Paşa Camii, kapalı Maraş şehri ve 2 bin yıllık Roma tiyatrosu ve birçok antik kalıntıya ev sahipliği tapan Salamis Harabeleri mutlaka görülmeli. 🍽️ KIBRIS’TA NE YENİR? - Kleftiko (Hırsız kebabı) - Hellim - Kıbrıs Köftesi - Molehiya - Piruhi - Pilavuna - Kolakas - Şeftali kebabı ✈️ ULAŞIM KKTC’ye sadece kimlik kartımızla giriş yapabiliyoruz. Doğu Karadeniz’de maalesef büyük çoğunluk eski evleri çürümeye bırakıp yerine çirkin, 4-5 katlı binalar dikerken, Erman tamamen kendi el emeğiyle bu evi yenilemiş, hem de çok zevkli bir şekilde.  📌 Buralarda artık bitmekte olan hayvancılığı da devam ettiriyor. Keşke herkes onun gibi olsa da, Karadeniz tam anlamıyla bir cennet olarak kalabilse. 📌 Sırf ona destek olmak için bile burada kalınır. Köy yaşantısını deneyimlemek de cabası. video_name: Güzel ülkemizin güzelliği en az bilinen şehirlerinden biri Burdur. 🤩🇹🇷 Burdur’un tarihi ve doğal güzelliklerini sizlerle de paylaşmak istedim :) 📍SAGALASSOS Ağlasun ilçesinde 1700 metre rakımda yer alan bu antik kent, Roma döneminde Pisidya bölgesinin en önemli şehri haline gelmiş ve bu dönemde çok zenginleşmiş. Antik kentte beni en çok etkileyen eser, İmparator Marcus Aurelius (M.S. 161-180) döneminde inşa edilmiş olan Antoninler Çeşmesi oldu. 📍SALDA GÖLÜ Deniz seviyesinden 1140 metre yükseklikteki Salda Gölü, Türkiye’nin en derim göllerinden biri. En dikkat çekici özelliği ise kesinlikle beyaz kumları ve turkuaz suyu. Biz Salda Gölü üzerindeki ilk balon turuna katıldık. Düzenli turların yakın zamanda başlaması planlanıyor. 📍KİBYRA ANTİK KENTİ Anadolu’nun antik çağdaki en görkemli stadyumuna ev sahipliği yapan Kibyra Antik Kenti’nde benim için en dikkat çekici eser kesinlikle antik odeonun zemininde, renkli mermerden yapılan 2000 yıllık Medusa mozaiği oldu. 📍BURDUR ARKEOLOJİ MÜZESİ Sadece 5 metre yüksekliğe sahip Marcus Aurelios ve Hadrianus heykellerini görmek için bile gidilir. Her iki heykel de Sagalassos’ta bulunmuş. Bunların dışında birçok başka heykel ve eser de bulunuyor. 🍽️ BURDUR’DA NE YENİ? Biz tarihi bir konakta hizmet veren TAŞ ODA GASTRONOMİ MUTFAĞI’nda yedik yemek. Burdur şiş, Burdur usulü tarhana çorbası ve ceviz ezmesi tadılması gereken lezzetler. ✈️ ULAŞIM Burdur’a birçok şehrimizde karayoluyla rahatlıkla ulaşabilirsiniz. Havayoluyla gitmek isteyenler ise Antalya’ya uçabilir. Antalya Havalima’nından Burdur şehir merkezine ulaşım sadece 1,5 saatte sürüyor. #burdur #türkiye #salda #turkey

video_name: HELADITOS DE BANANA, COCO Y CHOCOLATE: la combinación que nunca falla 🍌🍫 • Una receta simple y fresca, perfecta para tener lista en el freezer. Pero si querés ir a lo seguro, los vasitos descartables siempre están a la mano 😉 • 👩🏼‍🍳 INGREDIENTES: • 4 Bananas maduras 🍌 • 1 cda de Miel 🍯 • 1/2 taza de Bebida 100% vegetal de coco @laserenisimaok 🥥 • Esencia de Vainilla ✨ • Dulce de leche colonial de @laserenisimaok 🥄 • Chocolate semiamargo 🍫 • Fáciles, frescos y con ingredientes que seguro ya tenés en casa. video_name: TAMAGO SANDO Y ATÚN SANDO: un clásico japonés, fácil y rápido 🥪✨ •  Tenía muchas ganas de probar estos sando al estilo japonés para salir un poco de los sándwiches de siempre. Allá son re clásicos, los venden en estaciones y kioscos, pero bueno… como estamos medio lejos, los hice en casa y quedaron buenísimos. 🙌🏼 •  ✨ Tip: para el tamago, separé las claras de las yemas cuando ya estaban cocidas. Hice un puré con las yemas y piqué las claras bien chiquitas antes de mezclar con la mayo y la crema. Queda mucho más parejo y cremoso, se integra mejor con el pan y posta vale la pena tomarse ese ratito. • 👩🏼‍🍳 INGREDIENTES: Tamago Sando (huevo): • 8 huevos 🥚 • Mayonesa Natura 🥄 • Ciboulette 🌿 • Crema 🥛 • Sal 🧂 • Pimienta 🌶️ • Atún Sando: • 2 latas de atún 🐟 • Mayonesa Natura 🥄 • 1 tomate 🍅 • 1 palta 🥑 • 1/2 cebolla morada 🧅 • 30 ml de crema 🥛 • Para los dos: • Pan bien suave 🍞 • Quedan muy buenos así que vale la pena probarlos... ¡Contame cuál te animás a hacer! 😍✨ • #recetas #sandwich #japan

video_name: На меня наехал чеченец 😳 ДТП произошло не по моей вине, но я поехала дальше не по своей инициативе… А потому что мою приору тянула нива НА ТРОССЕ. И я попросту не могла остановиться.  Сообщив по рации Саше на ниве, что в меня въехали, тут же подъезжает этот мерседес и водитель уточнил «Я ВАС ВЪЕХАЛ?» «ДАВАЙТЕ ОСТАНОВИМСЯ ПОСМОТРИМ»… Я в шоке…приятном шоке, ведь в моей жизни такое впервые, что человек въехавший в в мою машину — хочет помочь и предлагает отполировать машину за его счёт. Не знаю как вас зовут, но спасибо вам, за вашу доброту. Пусть в мире будет как можно больше таких же добрых и честных людей 🙏🏻 #настятуман #авто #автоблогер

video_name: Pesawat kecil seperti Cessna atau Piper menggunakan bahan bakar khusus yang disebut AVGAS 100LL (Aviation Gasoline). Angka ‘100’ menunjukkan angka oktan yang sangat tinggi, artinya bahan bakar ini mampu menahan panas dan tekanan tinggi tanpa menyebabkan knocking (ledakan dini di mesin). Kenapa harus begitu? Mesin pesawat saat take-off dan climb bekerja pada putaran tinggi dan beban maksimum. Kalau diisi dengan bensin mobil biasa seperti Pertalite (oktan 90), mesin bisa mengalami knocking parah, tenaga turun, getaran berlebih, suhu cepat naik, hingga berisiko merusak mesin. Analoginya seperti motor sport 250cc yang dipaksa minum bensin oktan rendah. Memang bisa jalan, tapi performa berkurang, mesin cepat panas, dan umur komponen lebih pendek. Bedanya, kalau motor mogok bisa berhenti di pinggir jalan, sedangkan pesawat harus tetap aman di udara. Karena itu, pemilihan bahan bakar bukan sekadar pilihan, tapi soal keselamatan penerbangan.

bio:
Edu-kreator penerbangan
yang lagi balik ke kelas belajar Lalu Lintas Udara di @PPI Curug ✈️
video_name: Pesawat latih Piper Warrior menggunakan mesin andalan Pabrikan Lycoming O-320-D3G, mesin piston 4 silinder berpendingin udara. Walaupun kapasitasnya ‘hanya’ sekitar 160 tenaga kuda, mesin ini terkenal bandel, sederhana, dan mudah dirawat, cocok untuk pesawat latih yang dipakai sehari-hari. Mesin ini bisa dibilang ‘partner belajar’ yang sabar. Tahan dipakai untuk take-off pendek, touch-and-go berulang kali, hingga latihan stall dan manuver dasar. Justru karena ketangguhannya, banyak sekolah pilot di seluruh dunia menjadikan Piper Warrior sebagai kuda kerja mereka. Kalau mau dianalogikan, Lycoming O-320 itu seperti mesin motor touring 4-tak yang tahan banting. Bukan yang paling kencang, tapi bisa diajak jalan jauh, tangguh di berbagai kondisi, dan jarang rewel kalau dirawat benar. Bedanya, motor touring kalau mogok tinggal minggir, sedangkan Piper Warrior harus tetap terbang dengan aman. Itulah kenapa mesin ini dirancang simpel, teruji, dan bisa diandalkan. В комплекте 2 штуки, что позволяет оформить обе стороны. Они легко наносятся самостоятельно, обрезаются по размеру детали, а подробная инструкция входит в комплект. Они помогут не только придать автомобилю индивидуальный стиль, но и защитить от мелких царапин и замаскировать небольшие дефекты. Это оригинальный подарок в машину девушке, парню, мужу, папе. bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Since so many thought I blocked the vents with the @ragofabrication dash mount I figured may as well block the controls for them too hahahaha • I got this @midlandradio two way radio and figured this would give it a good place to mount as well as other stuff • The instructions said to pull apart the console but I used Rivnuts instead and it worked perfect. I didn’t have to pull anything apart • I don’t know about you but I loose Allen keys the week I get them, I’ve had this @gearwrenchtools T-handle set for years now and haven’t lost any of them. I feel like the labeled rack being on this tool chest keeps me inline • These @ragofabrication are available @4Runner Lifestyle

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Added this @Kimpex USA front and back windshield to the Maverick • This was a massive upgrade that took no time to install. The wind that goes through the cab is insane, it pulls on the helmets and there is no way to talk to each other • It’s made of 1/4” polycarbonate which is 250x stronger than glass and 25x stronger than acrylic. The reason I wanted this over glass is because I pull it on my flat deck and don’t want to crack the glass • I’ve sure been using this 1/4” @gearwrenchtools torque wrench a lot lately. It definitely fills the void that the 1/2” and 3/8” can’t get down to. Comes with a nice case as well  . . . #tools #kimpex #gearwrench #canam #maverickx3turborr

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: On our journey @Overland Expo we met @Slouch Couch  • This really got my interest because room can be tight when packing for an adventure but having a loveseat on hand would be so cool • So here’s the info It has a built in USB C rechargeable inflator/deflator. It inflates in 90 seconds. The material is 500D nylon condura so it can take a beating • The storage bag is way bigger than the couch so it’s super easy to get back in • They have it on their website right now $70 off making it $280 • It’s definitely become the favorite place to sit when we are out . . . #tools #camping #couch #furniture #slouchcouch

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: If you have installed a lot of rivets by hand you can definitely appreciate this tool • This Hilti Rivet tool runs on their Nuron battery platform. All you have to do is press the trigger and it does the rest. It keeps things consistent. • It has a spot for the different size nose pieces and has a container to catch the mandrel @Hilti North America  . . . #tools #construction #hiltipartner #hilti #hiltitools

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Gotta make sure you do the right prep work!! • I’m going to coat this floor and ramp but before that I need to sand down this floor and vacuum it many times to make sure the product will adhere properly • I decided to go with this 5” Bosch sander. No cord and I ran it with the bag • I went over this floor twice sanding it for over 30 min straight. I ran the 4ah core battery and by the end it was still showing 2 out of 5 bars • I had to empty the bag 3 times as well. It worked really good • Next I’ll put a few coats down on the floor. They use 3/4 plywood for the floor in the @Southland Trailer Corp.  @Bosch Power Tools  . . . #tools #construction #boschpartner #boschtools #construction

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: I never thought I’d be moving around my @Southland Trailers cargo trailer with a Makita drill • With the @Trailer Valet it’s possible! • I saw this like 5 years ago at a trade show and figured it would be handy! Wait till you see what I do with it next. @Makita Tools USA @Makita Canada Inc.  . . . #tools #construction #trailervalet #makita #makitatools

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Makita has just announced New 18v nailers! • Here is the angled 16g It can take 1-1/4 to 2-1/2 • So let’s toss in a compact battery and some 2-1/2 nails and see how it does • First some spruce with ease, I found some maple cutoffs and left in the 2-1/2. Now it is a full depth and as you can see it had no problem and even at that speed it kept them sinking at a consistent depth • Now bump fire isn’t normally something you use on a nailer like this but it does show the power of it, especially with that small battery • It has a light, a couple extra nose adapters and belt clip. Oh and it’s made in Japan @Makita Tools USA  . . . #tools #construction #makita #makitatools #makitapartner

bio: Murray Kruger
video_name: Adding the @kammok crosswing to the 4Runner • They have this side mount bracket that fit between my @intrepidcampgear tent and @Prinsu Design Studio roof rack • This awning is the fastest I’ve seen, literally a 3 second setup. bio: I'm journalist & motorcycle reviewer @otomotif_tv @otomotifweekly_ @gridoto.com
video_name: CUSTOMAXi 2025 seri pertama pecah banget! Berlangsung di Queen City Mall, Semarang, Jawa Tengah akhir pekan lalu (20-21 September 2025), totalnya ada 80 motor ikut adu keren konsep modifikasi.  Ada di video kali ini, kita lihat beberapa modifikasi yang keren-keren! Dari 2 kelas utama yaitu STREET MAXi dan SUPER MAXi. untuk masing-masing tipe motor mulai dari XMAX, NMAX, AEROX sampai LEXi. Bukan hanya kontes modifikasi, ada juga beberapa keseruan lainnya, seperti tatto temporary, photobooth AI, sampai live painting. Minggu ini, CUSTOMAXi 2025 giliran menyambangi Makassar, Sulawesi Selatan sebagai kota kedua. Minggu, 28 September 2025 bertempat di Mari Arcade, Mall Ratu Indah. Jangan sampai enggak dateng ya! #customaxi #customaxi2025 #yamahalexi #xmax #aerox #aeroxmodifikasi #aerox155 #nmax #nmaxmodifikasi

bio: I'm journalist & motorcycle reviewer @otomotif_tv @otomotifweekly_ @gridoto.com
video_name: Gak tau motor siapa hehe.. Tag ya kalau ada yang tahu ownernya. Kedua Honda NSR250R MC28 ini jadi salah satu magnet yang bikin langkah pengunjung berhenti di IMOS 2025.  Honda NSR250 MC28 ini masuk kategori racing replica dan dirilis pertama kali pada Oktober 1993. Pakai mesin 2-tak V-twin 249cc powernya 40 hp, transmisi 6 percepatan, dan sudah pakai fitur RC Valve. Salah satu fitur paling keren di zamannya adalah PGM Memory Card berfungsi sebagai microchip dengan engine mapping berbeda. Powernya bisa naik dari 40 hp ke 65 hp. Gokils.  Btw, yang merah sudah upgrade kaki-kaki pakai USD dan upgrade rem. Cakep ya! #nsr #nsr250 #nsr250r #nsr150 #hondansr

video_name: On 5 December 2012, at around 19:15 local time, the Baltic Ace, en route from Zeebrugge to Kotka with a cargo of 1,417 cars (mainly Mitsubishi from Japanese and Thai factories), collided with the Cypriot container ship Corvus J 65 nautical miles off the province of Zealand. The ship was holed and quickly sank. The container ship Corvus J remained afloat and took on board survivors from the sunken ship. Helicopters, coast guard boats and two patrol ships of the Royal Netherlands Navy took part in the rescue operation. 13 crew members were rescued, five bodies were found and six were missing. #acident #ship #sank #ferry #rescue

I felt mom guilt even writing this one, but I’ve been posting a lot of super happy content on here …So here’s a little reminder that social media doesn’t tell the full truth. Being her mom is the greatest thing I’ll ever do. I prayed for it. I also haven’t left the house alone in 4 months. Motherhood is not all sunshine and rainbows. video_name: No es con quién estar… es con quién ser. Porque para estar, cualquiera puede ocupar un lugar en tu vida. Pero para ser… ser auténtico, ser vulnerable, ser tu mejor versión… eso solo ocurre al lado de alguien que te da paz, que te impulsa a hacer cosas que no harías solo, y que cada día te recuerda que la felicidad está en las pequeñas cosas. La vida no va de coleccionar momentos con cualquiera… va de compartirlos con quien te hace sentir que eres todo su mundo. No es cuestión de compañía, sino de complicidad. No se trata de estar juntos… se trata de ser uno al lado del otro. No es solo con quién estar… es con quién puedes ser sin miedo, y aún así sentirte en casa. #amorperruno #viajarconperro

video_name: Volvería a elegir esta vida contigo en cada una de mis vidas ❤️🐶 Todo lo que amamos, algún día lo vamos a perder. Amar es aceptar que, tarde o temprano, dolerá. Qué en algún momento te romperá el corazón. Y aun así lo elegimos… porque sin amor, nada tendría sentido. Saber que, aunque algún día me rompas el corazón, lo volvería a elegir una y mil veces porque sé que habrá valido la pena. Porque tuvimos la suerte de vivir esto y esta magia no se encuentra en todas las vidas. Al final, no se trata del tiempo… se trata de la intensidad con la que vivimos, de la fuerza con la que sentimos y de cada instante que hacemos eterno. Aunque esta historia siempre termine igual, volvería a elegir esta vida en cada una de mis vidas. Porque vivirla contigo siempre será un REGALO. #amorperruno #viajarconperro

video_name: Se puede vivir sin un perro en tu vida ❤️🐶 Se puede vivir sin conocer a tu alma gemela o a tu mejor amigo. No necesitas a nadie que te reciba feliz cada vez que llegas a casa, ni a alguien que no se separe de ti en los buenos y en los malos momentos. El amor nunca ha sido cuestión de necesidad, sino de elección. Hay millones de formas de vivir nuestra vida, pero todas y cada una de ellas son mejores con un perrito a tu lado. 🐾✨ Sí, se puede vivir sin un perro a tu lado… pero la vida nunca sería la misma 💫 #amorperruno #viajarconperro

video_name: Mi hogar es ella ❤️🐶 Dicen que una de las cosas más importantes en la vida es encontrar nuestro hogar. Ese lugar donde sientes paz, seguridad y felicidad. Donde puedes ser tú mismo, sin barreras ni escudos. Al principio lo buscaba en cada lugar, convencido de que estaría en un sitio concreto… hasta que entendí que mi hogar es Hannita. Mi hogar tiene cuatro patitas y una mirada que lo dice todo. No importa dónde estemos, ni a dónde vayamos, ni lo lejos que estemos de casa. Nuestro hogar siempre será donde estemos juntos ❤️

video_name: ¿Con qué sueñan nuestros perros? ❤️🐶 La ciencia no lo sabe con certeza, pero muchos estudios creen que sueñan con sus recuerdos. Experiencias y momentos cercanos que han vivido recientes. Otros dicen que sueñan con nosotros: con nuestro olor, nuestros mimos y nuestros abrazos. Al final, para ellos, siempre somos lo más importante. Yo no sé con qué sueña ella, solo espero que sea con cada atardecer, con cada carrera y con cada abrazo que le doy. Pero, sobre todo, espero que al despertar o en sus sueños más profundos siempre sienta, en cada latido y en cada suspiro que para mí significa mi mundo entero ❤️🐶 #viajarconperro #amorperruno

bio:
Decidí dejarlo todo para viajar por el mundo con 
Hanna 🐺🌍🖤
Síguenos en IG 📱
video_name: Hoy miro atrás y no puedo creer todo lo que hemos vivido: nuestra primera aurora boreal, aquel viaje por Europa en coche, los meses en una cabaña en Laponia, en mitad de la nada… y tantos recuerdos grabados en mi corazón. Hanna me lo recuerda cada día: la felicidad no depende del lugar, sino de con quién compartes el camino. Yo no podría haber elegido mejor compañera de viaje… y de vida. ¿Listos para la próxima aventura? Porque creo que ha llegado el momento de soñar en grande… 🌍🐶❤️ #viajarconperro #amorperruno

bio:

video_name: Somos una vez en la vida ❤️🐶✨ En 4 meses estaremos en 2026, habrán pasado 6 años de una pandemia que nos quitó tanto y 5 años desde que nuestra vida cambió por completo.  En algún punto entre el ayer y el ahora, crecimos sin darnos cuenta. Aprendimos a soltar, a perder, a reconstruirnos… A veces pienso que todo pasa por algo y que tal vez todo eso que perdimos viaja  en cierta forma con nosotros y nos ha enseñado a valorar lo que realmente importa: A vivir el presente, valorar a quienes amamos, aprovechar cada instante… porque no somos eternos, solo somos una vez en la vida. #viajarconperro #amorperruno

video_name: Al mirar atrás y ver el camino recorrido con Vora, me doy cuenta de lo mucho que hemos avanzado juntos. Lo que en un principio parecía un reto enorme —que se concentrara, que dejara a un lado los impulsos y se enfocara en el juguete— hoy ya es una realidad. Y eso, aunque parezca un detalle, para mí significa muchísimo. Con la guía de Manel, poco a poco vamos subiendo escalones, buscando una evidencia cada vez más sólida, más limpia, más fina. Sé que todavía queda un largo camino, que el verdadero alto nivel está lejos, pero cada pequeño logro me recuerda que lo importante no es llegar rápido, sino avanzar. Lo más valioso de todo este proceso no es solo ver a Boran crecer, sino también lo que me enseña a mí: paciencia, constancia y confianza en el trabajo bien hecho. Al final, este viaje se resume en eso… avanzar, avanzar y avanzar. #k9 #UnidadCanina #PerrosPolicía #k9policia #malinois

By @Carlos Roca

video_name: ¡Podcast ya disponible! Episodio 61 de Roca Project: "MALDITA DR*G*: De Niño Adicto a Hombre Renacido" Host: @carlosrocax Invitado: @alexmanejo El crudo testimonio que os traemos hoy es la realidad que sufren muchas familias cada día. Álex Manejo empezó a consumir estupefacientes con tan solo 12 años. Venía de una familia estructurada, con todo aparentemente en orden. A los 20 años ya había sufrido 8 sobredosis y vivía debajo de un puente, bajo el yugo de su adicción. En este episodio de Roca Project, Álex Manejo comparte el testimonio real y crudo de sus años de adicción y consumo compulsivo de dr*g*s. cómo entró en la espiral de la dependencia, cómo gastó más de 800.000 euros en consumo, y qué ocurrió el día que decidió luchar por su vida y salir del pozo. Álex reflexiona sobre el daño que genera una adicción, en la persona y en el entorno, el papel fundamental de la familia y lo que realmente significa desintoxicarse para siempre. Hoy Álex hoy en día no solo está limpio y rehabilitado, sino que desde @clinica_antolex dedica su vida a inspirar y ayudar a cientos de personas atrapadas por la enfermedad de la adición que desean recuperar el control de sus vidas. Si estás consumiendo, o conoces a alguien que lo hace, este episodio no busca juzgar: busca encender una chispa. Hay salida y merece la pena buscarla. ► EPISODIO NUEVO CADA MIÉRCOLES A LAS 19:30 HORAS. #RocaProject #podcastclips #CarlosRoca #adiccion #crecimientopersonal

video_name: 📌 Detail fakta: Nama: Insiden sabuk pengaman wahana hiburan Sumber Video: 3D Garage Lokasi: Amerika Serikat, beberapa taman hiburan pernah mengalami kasus serupa Tahun: Kasus berbeda terjadi pada awal 2000-an hingga sekarang Status: Fakta, dengan catatan insiden keamanan pernah dilaporkan Kisah ini bermula dari sekelompok remaja yang awalnya hanya mencoba pengalaman bermain game VR di rumah. Permainan itu mensimulasikan sensasi naik wahana lengkap dengan sabuk pengaman khusus yang terasa begitu nyata. Sensasi tersebut membuat mereka penasaran dan ingin merasakan bagaimana pengalaman aslinya. Tanpa memberi tahu orang tua mereka, anak-anak itu diam-diam pergi ke sebuah taman hiburan yang memiliki wahana serupa. Di sana, mereka benar-benar mencoba wahana ekstrem yang mengangkat tubuh mereka tinggi ke udara. Awalnya, semuanya berjalan lancar. Mereka tertawa dan berteriak karena adrenalinnya terasa lebih dahsyat daripada sekadar permainan VR. Namun, di tengah perjalanan, terjadi sesuatu yang tak terduga. Sabuk pengaman salah satu anak tiba-tiba terbuka, membuat tubuhnya terhempas dari ketinggian. Tubuh anak itu jatuh menghantam tanah dengan keras. Kepanikan langsung pecah, orang-orang menjerit, dan operator wahana segera menghentikan permainan. Petugas medis yang berjaga di taman hiburan bergegas datang untuk memberikan pertolongan pertama. Meski kakinya mengalami cedera serius, beruntung anak itu masih selamat dari kejadian yang bisa saja merenggut nyawanya. Insiden ini membuat pihak taman hiburan langsung disorot. Pertanyaan besar muncul, bagaimana mungkin sabuk pengaman yang seharusnya dirancang untuk keselamatan bisa terbuka di tengah jalannya wahana. Perusahaan pengelola akhirnya diminta bertanggung jawab dan melakukan investigasi penuh terkait keamanan serta standar pengecekan peralatan sebelum digunakan. Cerita semacam ini menjadi pengingat keras tentang pentingnya keselamatan, baik dalam dunia hiburan virtual maupun nyata. Permainan VR bisa memberikan sensasi luar biasa, tapi tetap tidak bisa menyamai risiko dari pengalaman langsung di dunia nyata. Bagi keluarga, insiden ini menjadi pelajaran berharga agar selalu mengawasi anak-anak, dan bagi pengelola taman hiburan, menjadi dorongan untuk memperketat standar keamanan agar kejadian serupa tidak terulang. #faktaunik #kisahnyata #fakesituation  #fakebodyy⚠️  #fakesituation⚠️

video_name: 📌 Detail fakta: Nama: Skandal Permainan Karnaval Botol Susu Sumber Video: ROM Lokasi: Berbagai negara, terutama Amerika Serikat Tahun: Kasus tercatat sejak awal abad ke-20 hingga sekarang Status: Fakta yang sering ditemukan dalam investigasi kecurangan permainan karnaval Permainan melempar bola ke arah botol susu sudah lama jadi daya tarik utama di banyak karnaval. Dari luar, permainan ini terlihat sederhana, cukup jatuhkan semua botol dengan satu atau dua lemparan untuk membawa pulang hadiah besar. Namun, di balik keseruan itu, ternyata banyak permainan yang sengaja dimanipulasi agar hampir mustahil dimenangkan. Salah satu trik yang sering dilakukan adalah dengan menaruh pemberat tersembunyi di botol bagian bawah. Akibatnya, meskipun botol atas terlihat ringan dan mudah roboh, botol dasar tetap berdiri kokoh bahkan setelah terkena lemparan keras. Penonton yang tidak tahu rahasia ini akhirnya merasa frustrasi karena sudah mengeluarkan banyak uang tanpa peluang nyata untuk menang. Ada cerita terkenal tentang seorang pengunjung yang merasa curiga setelah berkali-kali gagal menjatuhkan semua botol. Ketika penjaga permainan lengah, ia nekat mengambil salah satu botol paling bawah dan menjatuhkannya ke lantai. Dari situ, rahasianya terbongkar, isi pemberat keluar, membuktikan bahwa permainan itu memang curang sejak awal. Insiden ini langsung memicu keributan di lokasi karnaval. Banyak pengunjung lain yang marah karena merasa ditipu. Pihak penyelenggara akhirnya dipaksa untuk bertanggung jawab, meskipun seringkali hanya berakhir dengan permintaan maaf atau pengembalian sebagian uang. Namun, kasus seperti ini membuat reputasi permainan karnaval jadi tercoreng dan menimbulkan pertanyaan soal kejujuran dalam hiburan rakyat. Hingga kini, banyak laporan serupa terus muncul. Beberapa kota bahkan membuat aturan khusus untuk mengawasi permainan karnaval agar tidak merugikan pengunjung. Mereka menciptakan sebuah mesin yang dirancang khusus untuk menyelesaikan rubik dengan kecepatan luar biasa. Kamera berteknologi machine vision dipasang di hadapan rubik untuk memindai seluruh warna pada permukaannya secara real time. Data visual itu lalu langsung diproses oleh algoritma pemecahan rubik tercepat yang pernah dibuat. Setelah pola rubik terdeteksi, komputer menghitung langkah paling efisien hanya dalam hitungan mikrodetik. Perintah kemudian dikirim ke motor berkecepatan tinggi yang menggerakkan sisi rubik dengan presisi luar biasa. Setiap putaran sisi hanya memakan waktu kurang dari satu milidetik, sehingga hampir mustahil dilihat dengan mata telanjang. Bagi penonton, rubik itu seakan langsung terselesaikan begitu saja. Catatan resminya, robot ini mampu menyelesaikan rubik hanya dalam 0,38 detik. Angka itu lebih dari 30 kali lipat lebih cepat dibandingkan rekor manusia tercepat di dunia. Bandingkan dengan pemegang rekor manusia yang rata-rata membutuhkan lebih dari 3 detik untuk menyelesaikan rubik. Oleh karena itu, proyek ini sekaligus menjadi bukti kemampuan teknologi dalam menciptakan harmoni antara kecerdasan buatan dan perangkat fisik. Rekor luar biasa ini kemudian menjadi viral, karena menunjukkan gambaran masa depan di mana mesin bisa melampaui keterampilan manusia bahkan dalam hal yang tampak sederhana seperti permainan rubik. Hingga kini, robot ini masih menjadi simbol perkembangan teknologi machine vision dan algoritma cerdas yang bisa diaplikasikan ke bidang lain, jauh lebih luas dari sekadar permainan. #faktaunik #fakebodyy⚠️  #robotika #fakesituation  #fakesituation⚠️

video_name: 📌 Detail fakta: Nama: Teknik strike bowling Sumber Video: ROM Lokasi: Digunakan di arena bowling seluruh dunia Tahun: Fakta yang dikenal sejak awal abad ke-20 Status: Fakta olahraga Bowling bukan hanya soal melempar bola ke pin, tetapi juga strategi dan teknik. Banyak pemula mengira bahwa target terbaik adalah pin tengah, karena posisinya berada di depan. Padahal, para pemain profesional tahu bahwa itu adalah kesalahan paling umum. Pin tengah justru akan sulit menjatuhkan pin lain jika bola hanya menghantamnya secara lurus. Teknik yang benar adalah mengincar area yang disebut "pocket," yaitu ruang kecil di antara pin nomor satu dan pin nomor tiga untuk pemain tangan kanan, atau pin nomor satu dan pin nomor dua untuk pemain tangan kiri. Saat bola mengenai area ini dengan sudut yang tepat, gaya pantulan dari pin akan menyebar ke samping dan mendorong pin lainnya jatuh beruntun. Inilah yang menciptakan kemungkinan besar terjadinya strike. Selain sudut lemparan, cara memegang bola juga penting. Pemain perlu memasukkan jari ke lubang bola, menarik tangan ke belakang, lalu melangkah maju dengan posisi satu kaki di depan sebagai tumpuan. Gerakan ini menjaga keseimbangan sekaligus memberikan tenaga tambahan pada lemparan. Ritme langkah yang tepat dapat membantu bola meluncur mulus menuju target. Pemain profesional bahkan menggunakan teknik putaran atau hook, di mana bola diputar sedikit saat dilepaskan. Putaran ini membuat bola melengkung menuju pocket dengan sudut yang lebih tajam. Dengan cara ini, peluang strike meningkat drastis, meskipun posisi awal lemparan tidak selalu lurus ke pin. Teknik pocket ini telah menjadi standar dalam dunia bowling profesional. Bahkan, banyak kompetisi tingkat dunia membuktikan bahwa konsistensi mengincar pocket jauh lebih efektif dibanding sekadar menabrak pin tengah. Jadi, bagi siapa pun yang ingin meningkatkan skor bowling, memahami strategi ini adalah langkah pertama menuju permainan yang lebih serius. #faktaunik #fakesituation⚠️  #bowlingstrike #fakebodyy⚠️  #fakesituation

Zion Williamson, bintang muda yang saat itu bermain untuk Duke University, mengalami kejadian langka ketika sepatunya tiba-tiba rusak hanya dalam hitungan detik setelah pertandingan dimulai. Saat ia sedang melakukan dribbling, bagian depan sepatu kirinya robek hingga membuat kakinya keluar dari dalam sepatu. Zion langsung terjatuh ke lantai dan mengalami cedera lutut yang cukup serius. Momen ini terjadi di pertandingan yang sangat penting, bahkan disaksikan langsung oleh mantan presiden Barack Obama yang duduk di tribun. Pertandingan baru berjalan 30 detik ketika insiden itu terjadi, dan seketika suasana stadion menjadi hening. Fans, pelatih, hingga media langsung mengkhawatirkan kondisi Zion, karena ia dikenal sebagai calon bintang besar NBA. Tidak butuh waktu lama, insiden sepatu ini viral di media sosial. Ribuan komentar membanjiri Twitter, Instagram, dan forum olahraga, banyak yang menertawakan kualitas sepatu Nike yang dipakai Zion. Beberapa bahkan menyebutnya sebagai "sepatu paling mahal yang gagal menjalankan tugasnya," mengingat Zion adalah pemain dengan potensi kontrak jutaan dolar. Bagi Nike, kejadian ini menjadi pukulan berat. Saham perusahaan sempat turun, dan reputasi mereka sebagai produsen sepatu olahraga kelas dunia ikut dipertanyakan. Meski akhirnya Nike bergerak cepat dengan memperbaiki desain sepatunya dan memberikan model khusus untuk Zion, kerugian citra sudah terlanjur menyebar luas. Insiden ini kini dikenal sebagai salah satu kejadian paling ikonik di dunia olahraga, bukan hanya karena cedera Zion, tetapi juga karena menunjukkan betapa besar dampak sebuah kegagalan produk di tengah sorotan publik global. #faktaunik #olahraga #fakesituation⚠️  #fakesituation  #fakesituation⚠️

bio:
Delving Deep into History's Mysteries.
With Your Guide, James 🗝️
video_name: 🏨 Built in 1888, the Fairmont Banff Springs Hotel has been called the “Castle in the Rockies.” But not every story within its stone walls is about luxury and grandeur. 👻 According to legend, a brutal family murder took place in Room 873. Guests later claimed to hear screams, see bloody handprints reappear on the walls, and encounter ghostly figures in the corridor. 🔒 The hotel eventually sealed the room, bricking over the doorway. To this day, visitors notice a gap where the door should be - a reminder of one of Canada’s most chilling mysteries. #history #historytok #historytiktok #hauntedplaces #hauntedtiktok

bio:
Delving Deep into History's Mysteries.
With Your Guide, James 🗝️
video_name: Hidden in plain sight in Banff 👀… half-fish, half-man, 100% nightmare fuel. Hoax or legend? You decide. 🧜‍♂️✨ Would you look this creature in the eye? Tucked away in Banff’s Trading Post is a creature you won’t forget 👀. The Banff Merman has been here for over 100 years - a bizarre taxidermy oddity, stitched together from fish and primate parts in the tradition of old ‘Fiji mermaids.’ 🧜‍♂️ Legend says Norman Luxton, ‘Mr. Banff,’ acquired it around 1915… and it’s been creeping out visitors ever since. Hoax, art, or evidence of something stranger? You decide. ✨ #history #historytok #historytiktok #mermaid #banff

bio:
Delving Deep into History's Mysteries.
With Your Guide, James 🗝️
video_name: Hidden in the churchyard of St Thomas à Becket in Box, Wiltshire, stands a curious pyramid-shaped tombstone. Its origins are cloaked in mystery, with local legend claiming it was built to stop the widow from ever dancing on her husband’s grave. Weathered and unmarked, it still rises like an echo of the past - a reminder that even in death, stories endure. #history #historytok #historytime #historytiktok #historylesson

bio:

video_name: ✨ Step into the very house where the night sky changed forever. At Bath’s Herschel Museum, William Herschel discovered Uranus in 1781, the first new planet found in over 2000 years. From this modest garden telescope came a discovery that reshaped our place in the cosmos 🔭🌍💫 #history #historytok #historytime #historytiktok #historylesson
